        " رَجُلٍ شَجَّ عَبْداً مُوضِحَةً قَالَ \"عَلَيْهِ نِصْفُ عُشْرِ قِيمَتِهِ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5266 - Imam Abu Abdullah (as) was asked about a man who inflicted a mudhiha (a wound exposing the bone) on a slave.\nImam (as) said: \"He is liable to pay half of one-tenth of the slave's value.\""
        ]
